{"tid":834019,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[NOW新聞]政府刊憲禁香港民族黨運作","createTime":"2018-09-24T02:26:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T02:26:48.000Z","uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a57b3638629ace875713d1f85621753943a97e7","tid":834019,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府刊憲禁止香港民族黨運作，香港民族黨召集人陳浩天表示暫時不予回應。<br />\n<br />\n政府刊憲，根據社團條例賦予保安局局長權力，命令禁止香港民族黨在港運作或繼續運作，即時生效。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨於2016年成立，召集人為陳浩天。有六大綱領，包括建立自由而獨立的香港共和國，廢除未經港人授權的基本法等。<br />\n<br />\n警方早前引用社團條例第八條，向保安局局長提出禁止香港民族黨運作，認為涉及維護、國家安全或公共安全，並給予廿一天作書面陳詞，民族黨期間多次申請延期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=321341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321341&d=9V0snLNjGsSXGZAvKmetolzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c752e8b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D321341&h=d47be989\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=321341</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨正式享有同三合會同等既法律地位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}